    "diffSummary": "Added the friends/contacts list. types/contact.rs adds the Contact DTO (no zca-rust dep). zalo/list_contacts maps zca-rust get_all_friends User into Contact (mapping confined to zalo) and sorts by display name. command/list_contacts reuses the stored session and returns Contact DTOs. The frontend adds a Danh bạ pane (ContactList) with avatars, search, A–Z grouping that scrolls, plus rail navigation (session.view) to switch chats/contacts; clicking a contact opens a DM. Also fixed a flexbox scroll bug (min-h-0 across the list/chat flex chains) and excluded .harness/** from the Vite dev watcher. CSP img-src widened to Zalo avatar CDNs. Verified live: 85 real contacts loaded; build/clippy/type-check pass; real browser validation passed.",
